scripts.deploy: npm run deploy-stivers && npm run deploy-tameron && npm run deploy-premier && npm run deploy-newcustomer
scripts.deploy-tameron: npm run build && aws s3 cp build s3://gptameron.com/ --recursive && aws cloudfront create-invalidation --distribution-id E1YPW3JQQ2QQ81 --paths "/*"
scripts.deploy-stivers: npm run build && aws s3 cp build s3://gpstivers.com/ --recursive && aws cloudfront create-invalidation --distribution-id EEZ12WJWK62SX --paths "/*"
scripts.deploy-premier: npm run build && aws s3 cp build s3://gp-premier.com/ --recursive && aws cloudfront create-invalidation --distribution-id EHOX2CBVSN2AB --paths "/*"
scripts.deploy-newcustomer: npm run build && aws s3 cp build s3://newcustomer.gpstivers.com/ --recursive && aws cloudfront create-invalidation --distribution-id E3IQU0KQR8MGZ6 --paths "/*"
